Important Update to Gegamo Chat

As part of recent security improvements, all direct messages, public chat history, and friend lists have been reset.

This reset was necessary to introduce stronger encryption and stricter session validation, ensuring your chats remain private and secure going forward.

We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience caused. Please note:

Your past chats are safe. We have securely backed them up, and you can request a copy by contacting support@gegamo.xyz
